":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32396,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/21\/seventy-two-doors-riba\/","url_meta":{"origin":30,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Seventy-two doors of usury include backbiting, slander","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara\u2019 ibn \u2018Azib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cUsury has seventy-two doors, the least of which is like a man who goes into his mother. The worst act of usury is for a man to attack the reputation of his brother.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/02\/03\/riba-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":30,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Allah curses all involved in usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah has cursed the one who consumes usury, its client, its witness, and its recorder. Usury and adultery do not become widespread among people but that they will become vulnerable to the punishment of Allah Almighty.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32182,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/avoid-seven-mortal-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":30,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Avoid sev